A child in appearance with the I.Q. of an adult.

32
00:01:33.770 --> 00:01:36.070
His name is Detective Conan!

33
00:03:22.027 --> 00:03:27.827
"The Suspects are Passionate Lovers (Part 1)"

34
00:03:31.727 --> 00:03:32.727
Don't tell me that...

35
00:03:32.727 --> 00:03:34.427
Did something happen to Doc?

36
00:03:36.827 --> 00:03:39.127
"Yoko Okino And Ryusuke Higo, Their Passionate Love Exposed!"

37
00:03:39.127 --> 00:03:42.827
Oh, come on! It's just a gossip article.

38
00:03:42.827 --> 00:03:44.127
You scared me out of my wits.

39
00:03:44.127 --> 00:03:46.527
What? Is this for real?

40
00:03:46.527 --> 00:03:49.327
-No joke? -They're a big couple!

41
00:03:49.327 --> 00:03:53.327
