47
00:04:04.027 --> 00:04:06.327
Rather, I don't think she's breathing.

48
00:04:08.127 --> 00:04:09.427
Wait a sec.

49
00:04:09.427 --> 00:04:13.227
If his partner is Yoko Okino, I'm sure he's...

50
