Get a hold of yourself, Dad!

52
00:04:20.227 --> 00:04:21.727
I thought so.

53
00:04:23.227 --> 00:04:25.527
Now, both their agencies

54
00:04:25.527 --> 00:04:28.527
haven't gotten a hold of either of them yet today,

55
