According to Higo's teammates,

57
00:04:34.527 --> 00:04:36.927
they seem to have graduated from the same high school

58
00:04:36.927 --> 00:04:38.427
and kicked it off well from there.

59
00:04:44.627 --> 00:04:46.327
Before you get so depressed,

60
00:04:46.327 --> 00:04:48.527
why don't you check on it and see if it's true?

61
00:04:48.527 --> 00:04:51.927
I mean, you do a lot of work on illicit relationships etc., don't you?

62
00:04:51.927 --> 00:04:53.027
Idiot!

63
00:04:53.027 --> 00:04:55.127
Detectives don't do things like investigating

64
00:04:55.127 --> 00:04:57.127
