65
00:04:57.127 --> 00:04:59.227
That's my policy!

66
00:04:59.227 --> 00:05:02.727
Then, will you investigate if I ask you to?

67
00:05:05.827 --> 00:05:07.727
Ai.

68
00:05:07.727 --> 00:05:08.727
Hey, hey.

69
00:05:08.727 --> 00:05:10.127
I'd like you to investigate

70
00:05:10.127 --> 00:05:13.827
