78
00:05:38.727 --> 00:05:42.727
Even their agencies can't get a hold of them, you know.

79
00:05:42.727 --> 00:05:44.227
Idiot!

80
00:05:44.227 --> 00:05:47.927
At times like this, safe comments are usually made public,

81
00:05:47.927 --> 00:05:49.827
but there are none,

82
00:05:49.827 --> 00:05:51.727
so it's highly likely that they're seeing each other again today

83
00:05:51.727 --> 00:05:54.627
without knowing that they're being rumored about!

84
00:05:54.627 --> 00:05:59.127
But wouldn't somebody normally e-mail or call them?

85
00:05:59.127 --> 00:06:03.727
Yoko's manager said that Yoko usually doesn't realize

86
00:06:03.727 --> 00:06:05.727
