90
00:06:12.827 --> 00:06:18.227
"Ryusuke Higo", "date" and "today's date".

91
00:06:18.227 --> 00:06:20.827
See? Here it is!

92
00:06:20.827 --> 00:06:23.327
Someone posted on their blog

93
00:06:23.327 --> 00:06:25.127
