240
00:14:00.994 --> 00:14:03.594
Don't you know? It's the talk of the town

241
00:14:03.594 --> 00:14:05.294
and causing a commotion on the gossip TV shows now.

242
00:14:05.294 --> 00:14:07.194
See?

243
00:14:07.194 --> 00:14:09.394
That the passionate love between Ms. Yoko Okino and Mr. Ryusuke Higo

244
00:14:09.394 --> 00:14:11.394
has been disclosed!

245
00:14:13.294 --> 00:14:15.094
Hey. So, what's the story?

246
00:14:15.094 --> 00:14:16.894
-What's the story? -What?

247
00:14:17.894 --> 00:14:20.894
Why are Mr. Mouri and the others here?

248
00:14:20.894 --> 00:14:23.394
It seems they just happened to be here.

249
00:14:23.394 --> 00:14:28.694
Why don't you try asking the other restaurant staff questions, too?

250
00:14:28.694 --> 00:14:30.394
